            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">Ph# 781-399-4354 | Fax # 781 207 0709 | </font></span><a href="http://www.xperttech.com/" title="blocked::http://www.xperttech.com/"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Cambria"><font size="3">www.xperttech.com</font></span></a></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial"><font size="3">IMPORTANT NOTE</font></span><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial">: If you have received this email in error or prefer not to receive such emails in future, please reply with &quot;&quot;</span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: red; font-family: Arial">Remove</span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: #1f497d; font-family: Arial">&quot;&quot; in the subject line and the email-id(s) to be removed. All removal requests will be honored ASAP.</span></font></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: green; font-family: Webdings">P </span><span style="font-size: 8pt; color: green; font-family: Calibri">Please consider the environment - do you really need to print this email?</span></font></div>
